---
import Base from "../layouts/Base.astro";
---
<Base title="Technology" description="Technology topics behind The Quotient Series">
  <section class="section page-shell">
    <h1>Technology</h1>
    <p>
      Both novels are filled to the brim with leading edge technology, extrapolated a few years into the future. Here is a
      sample of some of the technology topics covered in each novel. I cover several of these in my blog as well.
    </p>

    <div class="grid two-up">
      <article class="card">
        <h2>The Quantum Contingent</h2>
        <ul>
          <li>Quantum computing dangers</li>
          <li>Drone swarms and autonomous weapons</li>
          <li>Tesla Autopilot and Model X Plaid</li>
          <li>SpaceX, Starbase, and ocean launch bases</li>
          <li>Crypto, blockchain, and quantum blockchain</li>
          <li>Quantum networking and LEO satellite networks</li>
          <li>AI regulations and international AI accords</li>
          <li>Virtual reality and nanotechnology</li>
        </ul>
      </article>

      <article class="card">
        <h2>Quantum Time</h2>
        <ul>
          <li>Quantum entanglement and time</li>
          <li>Optimus and advanced robotics</li>
          <li>Invisibility cloak concepts</li>
          <li>Cryonics</li>
          <li>Augmented reality, virtual reality, and the metaverse</li>
          <li>Large language models like ChatGPT</li>
        </ul>
      </article>
    </div>
  </section>
</Base>
